items.description: This repository contains a solution to generate EAN-13(GTIN-13) barcodes based on GS1 Brazil rules. The generated barcode is compatible with barcode readers and can be used in inventory management, sales and product control systems.

items.name: Bookstore-system
items.description: The Bookstore Management System is a C++ program to manage book collections. Features include adding, displaying, sorting (name, author, price), searching (binary search), and removing books using a linked list. It ensures file persistence, efficient algorithms, and performance monitoring, making it ideal for learning or small bookstores.
